GET http://0.0.0.1:5000/role/<string:role_id>
content-type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

###
#@name role_autocomplete_by_name
POST http://0.0.0.0:5000/role/autocomplete
content-type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "search": "Some string"
}

